player for various audio and video formats (MPEG-1, MPEG-2, \
MPEG-4, DivX, mp3, ogg, and more) as well as DVD's, VCD's, \
and various streaming protocols. It can also be used as a \
server to stream in unicast or multicast in IPv4 or IPv6 \
on a high-bandwidth network. VLC also has the ability to \
transcode media on-the-fly for streaming or saving to disk."
